===Adjective===
'''intransigent'''

# Unwilling to [[compromise]] or [[moderate]] a position; [[unreasonable]]; [[irreconcilable]]; [[stubborn]].
#: ''Don't waste your time trying to change his mind, he's completely '''intransigent'''.''

